data.description: 2009 built single family in great location with updates galore! New LVP flooring upper and lower level 2021/2022, refaced upper cabinets and all new lower cabinets replaced with soft close wood drawers 2021, granite countertops 2021, new dishwasher/sink/disposal 2021, subway tile backsplash 2023, new washer and dryer 2020, commercial grade rain gutters installed 2021, new expansive 16x24 deck 2023. Deck to be completed prior to close (all permits pulled and will be closed prior to closing). Best of both worlds with a detached single family home and an association covering lawn care. Walking distance to DT Rosemount and Hope Fieldhouse.
